307
00:28:45,613 --> 00:28:48,491
C'est tout? La leçon est terminée?

308
00:28:48,573 --> 00:28:50,564
Loin de là.

309
00:28:51,213 --> 00:28:52,726
Viens.

310
00:28:57,413 --> 00:28:59,643
